{
  "_doc": "Dominaria United (DMU) Draft + Collector recipes. Source: https://magic.wizards.com/en/news/feature/collecting-dominaria-united-2022-08-18 . Full lineup is Set + Draft + Collector Booster; per assignment we model only Draft + Collector and set authoritative:true. Ignored: Set Booster, Jumpstart, Commander, Bundle, Prerelease. Draft Booster = 15 cards (10 common, 3 uncommon, 1 rare/mythic, 1 basic land); a traditional foil of any rarity replaces a common 33% of the time; every pack has a guaranteed legendary creature and ~1-in-3 legends carry the showcase stained-glass treatment (approximated as 'showcase' filter on a portion of the rare/mythic + foil outcomes). Collector Booster = 15 cards. Sub-set codes: DMU main, PDMU promos/Lost Legends approximation, TDMU tokens, ADMU art series. Legends Retold box toppers live in a separate Scryfall set (DMU Commander box toppers); since the exact code isn't confidently known they are approximated as DMU cards with the etched_foil filter and noted here. The Collector textured-foil slot now targets the textured_foil filter (promo_types=textured) exactly rather than plain foil. DMU has no retro frame cards — the Legends Retold treatment is foil-etched (etched_foil filter), not retro. Remaining approximations: Phyrexian-language alt-art approximated as borderless; Lost Legends (3% of Collector Boosters) approximated via the special_guest filter on PDMU; serialized Hidetsugu/Ajani ultra-rare drops omitted as sub-1% noise. AUDIT 2026-06: Legends Retold outcomes re-pointed from etched_foil (matched nothing — prints lack the etched flag) to the dmu_legends_retold collector range; PDMU Lost Legends outcome unfiltered (the promo set IS the sheet; specialguests promo tag absent).",
